fca.org.au/whatsnew.php |title=THE BLACK BALLOON SOARS AGAIN AT THE 2008 AFCA FILM AWARDS \u2013 MEDIA RELEASE |accessdate=2011-01-03 |work=Australian Film Critics Association |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025203835/http://afca.org.au/whatsnew.php |archivedate=2008-10-25 }}</ref>\n| Best Overseas Film\n!\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" | February 10, 2008\n| rowspan=\"9\" | [[61st British Academy Film Awards|BAFTA Awards]]<ref name=\"BAFTAAwards\">{{cite web |url=http://www.bafta.org/awards/film/film-awards-nominees-in-2008,224,BA.html |title=BAFTA Film Award Winners in 2008 |accessdate=2008-02-19 |work=British Academy of Film and Television Arts |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/662qUu2zg?url=http://www.bafta.org/film/awards/2008,2380,BA.html |archivedate=2012-03-09 }}</ref>\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Film|Best Film]]\n!\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Direction|Best Direction]]\n| Paul Thomas Anderson\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Adapted Screenplay|Best Adapted Screenplay]]\n| Paul Thomas Anderson\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Leading Role|Best Actor in a Leading Role]]\n| Daniel Day-Lewis\n| {{Won}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role|Best Actor in a Supporting Role]]\n| [[Paul Dano]]\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Film Music|Best Film Music]]\n| Jonny Greenwood\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Production Design|Best Production Design]]\n| Jack Fisk, Jim Erickson\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]]\n| Robert Elswit\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| [[BAFTA Award for Best Sound|Best Sound]]\n| Matthew Wood\n| {{Nom}}\n|-\n| January 10, 2009\n| [[Belgian Syndicate of Cinema Critics]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.lalibre.be/culture/divers/article/469209/breves.html |title='Eldorado' s'offre le Prix Cavens |work=La Libre Belgique |date=December 20, 2008 |accessdate=October 26, 2012 |language=French}}</ref